#. <section class="sutta" id="an5.122"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.122:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.122:0.2"
msgid "13. Gilānavagga"
msgstr "13. Sick"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.122:0.3"
msgid "122. Satisūpaṭṭhitasutta"
msgstr "122. Mindfulness Well Established"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an5.122:1.1"
msgid ""
"“Yo hi koci, bhikkhave, bhikkhu vā bhikkhunī vā pañca dhamme bhāveti pañca "
"dhamme bahulīkaroti, tassa dvinnaṃ phalānaṃ aññataraṃ phalaṃ pāṭikaṅkhaṃ—"
msgstr ""
"“Mendicants, any monk or nun who develops and cultivates five qualities can "
"expect one of two results:"

msgctxt "an5.122:1.2"
msgid "diṭṭheva dhamme aññā, sati vā upādisese anāgāmitā."
msgstr ""
"enlightenment in the present life, or if there’s something left over, non-"
"return."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an5.122:2.1"
msgid "Katame pañca?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "an5.122:2.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhuno ajjhattaññeva sati sūpaṭṭhitā hoti dhammānaṃ "
"udayatthagāminiyā paññāya, asubhānupassī kāye viharati, āhāre paṭikūlasaññī, "
"sabbaloke anabhiratasaññī, sabbasaṅkhāresu aniccānupassī."
msgstr ""
"It’s when a mendicant has well established mindfulness inside themselves in "
"order to understand the arising and passing away of phenomena, meditates "
"observing the ugliness of the body, perceives the repulsiveness of food, "
"perceives dissatisfaction with the whole world, and observes the "
"impermanence of all conditions."

msgctxt "an5.122:2.3"
msgid ""
"Yo hi koci, bhikkhave, bhikkhu vā bhikkhunī vā ime pañca dhamme bhāveti ime "
"pañca dhamme bahulīkaroti, tassa dvinnaṃ phalānaṃ aññataraṃ phalaṃ "
"pāṭikaṅkhaṃ—"
msgstr ""
"Any monk or nun who develops and cultivates these five qualities can expect "
"one of two results:"

msgctxt "an5.122:2.4"
msgid "diṭṭheva dhamme aññā, sati vā upādisese anāgāmitā”ti."
msgstr ""
"enlightenment in the present life, or if there’s something left over, non-"
"return.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.122:2.5"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
